title: Bobby Fears Something + 50 States Test + Raymundo’s Controversial Tweet Update
itunes:title: Bobby Fears Something + 50 States Test + Raymundo’s Controversial Tweet Update
description:
Bobby talks about fearing something he has to do for his NatGeo show and it’s CRAZY! Bobby quizzes the show to see who can get the most of the 50 states by memory. We talk to Craig Campbell about his crazy spider bite. Plus, the latest development in the tweet Raymundo sent out about Carly Pearce and Michael Ray’s divorce!
